<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kum sang vaihawm ni hung naiin,
 Kei banga liengthei albang vaite'n;
 Thilsiem tincheng leh lei Sapchuomte hin,
 Ngaiin ka thil ui, Isu hung naiin,

[V2]
 Lalpa, hungkum in, ka hun ngai ui,
 Salem Zion tang lopi Lalpa;
 Chun-leh-zuo leh phungguol a chieh zo tau,
 Aw, ka Lal nunnem ka lu hung lieh in.

[V3]
 2. Phamsa ngai in ka kap, Lalpa
 Khawvel Aigupta gamah ka vai;
 Lalpa na vangsakna lul ka chan hi
 Pak bang lawp manlo in muol a liem ie.

[V4]
 3. Phamsa ngai ka kah lai hinle,
 Lili pak tat sate a lennau;
 Ginna'n thangvan khu ka vak gal thila,
 Lungdeih te lenna Zion tang a lang.

[V5]
 4. Ka ngai Jerusalem Zion,
 Thiemgau, martar thisan a tatte;
 Phamsa thokit leh ka lungtup gam khu,
 Muh ka nuom ngei Aw lungdeih a kimnau.</lyrics>
<title>Isu Hung Nai In</title>
<author>Lienrum</author>
<hymn_number>291</hymn_number>
</song>